## Next Steps for Users
After deployment to Vercel:
1. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard (Analytics tab)
2. Deploy the application using `vercel deploy`
3. Visit the deployed site and check browser Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/view`
4. View analytics data in the Vercel dashboard under the Analytics tab

## Notes
- The implementation preserves all existing functionality
- No route support is needed for this simple single-page application
- The Analytics component will automatically track page views when deployed to Vercel
- In development mode, analytics will run in development mode and won't send production data
